{"Title": "Texygen: A benchmarking platform for text generation models", "Year": 2018, "Source": "Int. ACM SIGIR Conf. Res. Dev. Inf. Retr., SIGIR", "Volume": null, "Issue": null, "Art.No": null, "PageStart": 1097, "PageEnd": 1100, "CitedBy": 35, "DOI": "10.1145/3209978.3210080", "Link": "https://www.scopus.com/inward/record.uri?partnerID=HzOxMe3b&scp=85051482023&origin=inward", "Abstract": "\u00a9 2018 ACM.We introduce Texygen, a benchmarking platform to support research on open-domain text generation models. Texygen has not only implemented a majority of text generation models, but also covered a set of metrics that evaluate the diversity, the quality and the consistency of the generated texts. The Texygen platform could help standardize the research on text generation and improve the reproductivity and reliability of future research work in text generation.", "AuthorKeywords": ["Benchmarking", "Evaluation metrics", "Text generation"], "IndexKeywords": ["Benchmarking platforms", "Evaluation metrics", "Reproductivity", "Text generations"], "DocumentType": "Conference Proceeding", "PublicationStage": null, "OpenAccess": 0, "EID": "2-s2.0-85051482023", "SubjectAreas": [["Software", "COMP", "1712"], ["Computer Graphics and Computer-Aided Design", "COMP", "1704"], ["Information Systems", "COMP", "1710"]], "AuthorData": {"57195775691": {"Name": "Zhu Y.", "AuthorID": "57195775691", "AffiliationID": "60025084", "AffiliationName": "Shanghai Jiao Tong University"}, "57214817481": {"Name": "Lu S.", "AuthorID": "57214817481", "AffiliationID": "60025084", "AffiliationName": "Shanghai Jiao Tong University"}, "57203438162": {"Name": "Zheng L.", "AuthorID": "57203438162", "AffiliationID": "60025084", "AffiliationName": "Shanghai Jiao Tong University"}, "57199054815": {"Name": "Guo J.", "AuthorID": "57199054815", "AffiliationID": "60025084", "AffiliationName": "Shanghai Jiao Tong University"}, "56108513500": {"Name": "Zhang W.", "AuthorID": "56108513500", "AffiliationID": "6002508